OverviewHello, I’m Sergiy and have a pleasure to present the Hands Free Selfie Rig to you. We are a team of friends who like sports. My personal preference is downhill skiing and biking. It can be a challenge to take a video of yourself doing sports. Holding an ordinary selfie stick takes one hand out of the action which is not acceptable in some sports like skiing, biking and many others. This is why we’ve designed Q-Rig -  the Hands Free Selfie Rig which holds the selfie sticks for you. Specifically, the selfie sticks are mounted on a helmet. Q-Rig is light and doesn’t obstruct head movement.The unique self-leveling feature stabilizes camera for better video. No more hands “glued” to the selfie stick on your videos. Both of your hands are free for action.To make design simple, robust, waterproof and affordable there are no electronics and batteries.Q-Rig is crowd friendly. Selfie sticks are easy to collapse when you are in a chair lift or just done recording. As Q-Rig is lightweight it can be left on the helmet even if not in use.Q-Rig is highly customizable. Another selfie sticks can be installed and it’s easy to replace parts if they were broken in action.3D printing technology allowed us to go through a series of different designs and test all of them. What you see is a fully functional prototype.Q-Rig benefitsTo summarize the advantages (our goals during the design phase) of Q-Rig:
Hands free;
Lightweight, shouldn’t obstruct head movement;
Self-stabilized (patent pending);
Flexible/modular, allow use of wide range of existing equipment like selfie sticks;
Waterproof;
Easy to use and transport (foldable);
Easy to take apart (for cleaning);
Flexible packaging: the whole set-up or just the pivot mount (Q-Rig core);
Made in USA;
Affordable;
Q-Rig was tested with GoPro cameras, but widely available adapters allow use of any action camera including 3600 ones.Set-upsThere are two ways to set-up Q-Rig: self-stabilized and high point of view.Self-stabilized set-upWith this set-up selfie sticks are pointing slightly down and Q-rig center of gravity is lower than the mounting point. This results in self-leveling, supports additional image stabilization and doesn't restrict head movements.Second camera or a water tight case filled with water can be used as a counterweight. There is no limit to your creativity. It's possible to use a sound system as a counterweight or you can get rid of the camera altogether, mount two sound systems and enjoy a stereo sound :-)High point of view set-upIn some cases it is important to make video from a higher point of view. I such case Q-Rig core is mounted "upside down" and selfie sticks are pointing slightly up. Due to the higher center of gravity the self-leveling feature is off, but point of view is higher.To ensure the secure coupling between Q-Rig core and GoPro mounting buckle the thumb screw #1 should be tighten up with GoPro wrench.Thumb screw #2 can be tightened to dampen or prevent movement of the upper part of the Q-Rig (the selfie stick holder.)PackagingThere are 6 packages.#1 Golden CoreThe package includes:
Q-Rig Core with "Golden" clamps;
GoPro wrench (to tight GoPro screws);
Add your selfie sticks, counterweight, camera and you are ready to go.#2 Black Diamond CoreThe package includes:
Q-Rig Core with Black clamps;
GoPro wrench (to tight GoPro screws);
Add your selfie sticks, counterweight, camera and you are ready to go.#3 Golden Hero CompleteThe package includes:
Q-Rig Core with "Golden" clamps;
Watertight Hero case as a counterweight;
GoPro wrench (to tight GoPro screws);
2x selfie sticks with GoPro mounts;
Add your camera and you are ready to go.#4 Golden Session CompleteThe package includes:
Q-Rig Core with "Golden" clamps;
Watertight Session case as a counterweight;
GoPro wrench (to tight GoPro screws);
2x selfie sticks with GoPro mounts;
Add your camera and you are ready to go.#5 Black Diamond Hero CompleteThe package includes:
Q-Rig Core with Black clamps;
Watertight Hero case as a counterweight;
GoPro wrench (to tight GoPro screws);
2x selfie sticks with GoPro mounts;
Add your camera and you are ready to go.#6 Black Diamond Session CompleteThe package includes:
Q-Rig Core with Black clamps;
Watertight Session case as a counterweight;
GoPro wrench (to tight GoPro screws);
2x selfie sticks with GoPro mounts;
Add your camera and you are ready to go.Let's do it!We are passionate about supporting US manufacturers, so the plan is to produce Q-Rig core right here in US.Crowdfunding will allow starting the mass production and bring our product to the market at a very affordable price. This is where we need your help!Supply chain is ready. The missing parts are molds for the injection molding which will be used to manufacture Q-Rig core. Injection molding company will use the same 3D models of the parts that were used in 3D printing process, so starting production is the matter of signing the contract.We believe that you deserve to have and share video of your most exciting moments. This is why we created the Q-Rig - a hands-free selfie rig that is lightweight, easy to use, and affordable. Get the word out and let Q-Rig become a reality!
